insert into diksha_tpd_mapping(uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status,created_on,updated_on) select uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status,now(),now() from (SELECT uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status, row_number() over (partition by uuid,state,district_name,school_name,school_id,status) as rn from diksha_tpd_mapping_temp) sq Where rn =1 on conflict(uuid,school_id) do update set uuid=excluded.uuid,state=excluded.state,district_name=excluded.district_name, school_name=excluded.school_name,school_id=excluded.school_id,status=excluded.status,updated_on=now()

insert into diksha_api_summary_roll_up as b (date,file_url,expiry_time,cqube_process_status,created_on) values('${diksha_api_summary_rollup_date}', '${diksha_api_summary_rollup_file_url}', '${diksha_api_summary_rollup_file_expiry_time:format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS','IST')}', 'SUBMITTED', '${now():format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS')}')
ON CONFLICT (date) do update set file_url='${diksha_api_summary_rollup_file_url}',expiry_time='${diksha_api_summary_rollup_file_expiry_time:format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS','IST')}', updated_on='${now():format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS')}' where b.cqube_process_status <> 'SUCCESS'

select "Collection Id" as collection_id, "Collection Name" as collection_name,state,"Enrolment Date" as enrolment_date,"Batch Id" as batch_id,"Batch Name" as batch_name, "completion Date" as completion_date,"certificate status" as certificate_status,"Org Name" as org_name,progress,"total score" as total_score, "user uuid" as uuid from flowfile

UPDATE files_ingestion SET status = '${status:isNull():ifElse('OK','${status}')}', storage_date = '${now():format("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS")}', storage_name = '${filename}' WHERE ff_uuid = '${files_uuid}';
update diksha_api_meta set total_files='${fragment.count}',updated_on='${now():toNumber():format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS')}' where ff_uuid='${ff_uuid:trim()}';

select ff_uuid,request_channel,request_id,request_status,cqube_process_status,tag from diksha_api_meta where request_status='SUBMITTED' or request_status='SUCCESS' and cqube_process_status='SUBMITTED' order by requested_on
update diksha_api_meta set cqube_process_status='SUCCESS', updated_on='${now():toNumber():format('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS')}' where ff_uuid='${ff_uuid:trim()}' and files_emitted=total_files;
